<lemma xml:id="r_potential-energy-diagrams">
	<title>Potential Energy Diagrams</title>
	<statement>
	<p>A potential energy diagram is a graph of the potential energy <m>U(x)</m> vs. <m>x</m> for some system of interest.</p>
	</statement>
	</lemma>

<p>On a potential energy diagram, it is often useful to indicate the total energy of a system.</p>

