<answer>
<definition>
	<title>Energy Bar Chart</title>
	<statement>
	<p>An energy bar chart is a graphical representation where each form of energy in a system is represented by a vertical bar.  It is often common to draw a different bar chart for each instant of interest.</p>
	</statement>
	</definition>
